Behaviour doesn't match description -- per the commit title, this should be:

```c++
    if (pfrom.fSuccessfullyConnected) {
        if (!m_chainparams.GetConsensus().signet_blocks) {
            pfrom.fDisconnect = true;
        }
        return;
    }
```

If you want the behaviour that's implemented, should be described as "support sendaddrv2 after verack on signet only fo
